snippet.textDisplay:
Hey I think that this might’ve already been said, but y’all need to stop complaining about the fortnite loot. I think that side grading is the best way to fix loot rng. Think about it; seasons 8-10 had a crap ton of items, and there were barely any consumables. With side grading, all of the popular guns will be back, like the tac smg, silenced sky, heavy shotgun, hunting rifle, and more. This doesn’t explain the lack of movement, or any movement items, like shockwaves or impulses, but it’s a start to getting fortnite back to the way everyone enjoyed.

Ps not an Epic worker; I would be fired at that case for spilling the tea of what Epic has in store. I think it just seems obvious.
